---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { events, profile, works } from "../data/profile";
import blogPosts from "../data/blog-posts.json";
---

<BaseLayout title={`${profile.name} · AI product builder`}>
  <article class="home wrapper">
    <h1 class="sr-only">{profile.name}</h1>

    <img class="home-avatar" src="/images/avatar-zhihu.jpg" alt="Wujia / Haibo Wu" />

    <div data-lang-content="en">
      <p>I’m Wujia / Haibo Wu. I build AI products at the edge of commerce, creative workflows, open source, and personal memory.</p>

      <p>My current work is split between <a href={profile.links.weshop}>WeShop AI</a>, a commercial image and video generation platform for global e-commerce teams, and <a href={profile.links.memex}>Memex</a>, an open-source local-first AI journal for personal memory.</p>

      <p>Before this AI cycle, I spent more than a decade building internet products close to users, commerce, content, search, recommendation, advertising, SaaS delivery, and commercialization.</p>

      <p>That background shapes how I think about AI: demos are easy; durable products have to enter workflows, build on owned data, control quality, and earn trust over time.</p>

      <p>Start with <a href="/works/">work</a>, <a href="/blog/">writing</a>, <a href="/events/">events</a>, or <a href="/about/">about</a>. You can also find me on <a href={profile.links.github}>GitHub</a>, <a href={profile.links.linkedin}>LinkedIn</a>, and <a href={profile.links.zhihu}>Zhihu</a>.</p>
    </div>

    <div data-lang-content="zh">
      <p>我是 Wujia / Haibo Wu，做 AI 产品，也长期写一些关于产品、技术和商业化的思考。</p>

      <p>现在主要做两件事：<a href={profile.links.weshop}>WeShop AI</a>，面向全球电商的 AI 图片与视频生成平台；<a href={profile.links.memex}>Memex</a>，一个开源、local-first 的个人 AI 日志。</p>

      <p>在这一轮 AI 之前，我有十多年互联网产品经验，做过搜索、推荐、广告、电商内容、SaaS 交付和商业化。</p>

      <p>这些经历让我更关心 demo 之后的事情：AI 应用如何进入真实工作流，沉淀自有数据，稳定控制质量，并被长期信任。</p>

      <p>可以从 <a href="/works/">作品</a>、<a href="/blog/">文章</a>、<a href="/events/">活动</a> 或 <a href="/about/">经历</a> 开始看，也可以在 <a href={profile.links.github}>GitHub</a>、<a href={profile.links.linkedin}>LinkedIn</a> 和 <a href={profile.links.zhihu}>知乎</a> 找到我。</p>
    </div>

    <h2>
      <span data-lang-content="en">Selected work</span>
      <span data-lang-content="zh">精选作品</span>
    </h2>
    <ul class="plain-list">
      {works.map((work) => (
        <li>
          <a href={work.href}>{work.title}</a>
          <span data-lang-content="en">{work.summary}</span>
          <span data-lang-content="zh">{work.summaryZh}</span>
        </li>
      ))}
    </ul>
    <p>
      <a href="/works/">
        <span data-lang-content="en">All work</span>
        <span data-lang-content="zh">全部作品</span>
      </a>
    </p>

    <h2>
      <span data-lang-content="en">Selected posts</span>
      <span data-lang-content="zh">精选文章</span>
    </h2>
    <ul class="plain-list">
      {blogPosts.slice(0, 3).map((post) => (
        <li>
          <a href={`/blog/${post.slug}/`}>
            <span data-lang-content="en">{post.titleEn}</span>
            <span data-lang-content="zh">{post.titleZh}</span>
          </a>
          <span data-lang-content="en">{post.excerptEn}</span>
          <span data-lang-content="zh">{post.excerptZh}</span>
        </li>
      ))}
    </ul>
    <p>
      <a href="/blog/">
        <span data-lang-content="en">All writing</span>
        <span data-lang-content="zh">全部文章</span>
      </a>
    </p>

    <h2>
      <span data-lang-content="en">Events and interviews</span>
      <span data-lang-content="zh">活动与访谈</span>
    </h2>
    <ul class="plain-list">
      {events.slice(0, 3).map((item) => (
        <li>
          <a href={item.href}>
            <span data-lang-content="en">{item.titleEn}</span>
            <span data-lang-content="zh">{item.titleZh}</span>
          </a>
          <span data-lang-content="en">{item.date} · {item.kind} · {item.source}. {item.noteEn}</span>
          <span data-lang-content="zh">{item.date} · {item.kindZh} · {item.sourceZh}. {item.note}</span>
        </li>
      ))}
    </ul>
    <p>
      <a href="/events/">
        <span data-lang-content="en">All events</span>
        <span data-lang-content="zh">全部活动</span>
      </a>
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
